          Happening 
        and performance artist. His career was characterized by passionate, even acrimonious public debate, but he is now regarded as one of the most influential German artists of the second half of the 20th century.
      %p
        %a{:href=>"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e5UXAqpSJDk"}
          Watch a video of him on YouTube 
