  - elsif params[:name] == "abramovic"
    .span12
      %h1
        Photographs of Marina Abramovic
    .span6
      %p
        Marina Abramović (born November 30, 1946) is a New York-based Serbian performance artist who began her career in the early 1970s. Active for over three decades, she describes herself as the "grandmother of performance art". 

      %p
